4. Data Modelling

User
Attributes:
user_id (Primary Key)
name
email (Unique)
password_hash
role (e.g., buyer, seller, admin)
profile_picture
created_at
updated_at
Product
Attributes:
product_id (Primary Key)
seller_id 
title
description
price
category_id 
images (e.g., URLs or paths)
stock_quantity
created_at
updated_at

5. User Stories
 Buyer User Stories
Account Creation and Login
As a buyer, I want to register an account using my email or social login so that I can access the marketplace and make purchases.
Product Browsing
As a buyer, I want to browse products by category so that I can find items I’m interested in.
Product Details
As a buyer, I want to view detailed information about a product, including images, description, and price, so that I can make informed purchasing decisions.
    Ratings and Reviews
As a buyer, I want to leave a review and rating for products I’ve purchased so that I can share my feedback with other users.
Seller User Stories
Account Creation and Login
As a seller, I want to create a seller account so that I can list products and manage my sales.
Product Listing
As a seller, I want to create and publish product listings with details such as title, description, price, and images so that buyers can see and purchase my products.



6. Mockups

 Homepage

Header: Includes navigation links (Home, Categories, About Us, Contact), search bar, and user login/signup buttons.
Footer: Includes links to privacy policy, terms of service, and social media icons.


Product Detail Page
Features:
Product Images: Main image with thumbnails of additional images.
Product Information: Title, price, description, and seller information.
Add to Cart Button: Prominent button to add the product to the shopping cart.
Reviews Section: User reviews and ratings for the product.
Visuals:
Layout: Detailed view with large images and clear sections for product info and reviews.

